ingredients: WHITE DOUGH: ENRICHED DURUM WHEAT FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, FERROUS SULFATE, THIAMIN, MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WATER, EGGS, SOYBEAN OIL, SALT, TURMERIC. GREEN DOUGH: ENRICHED DURUM WHEAT FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, FERROUS SULFATE, THIAMIN, MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID); SPINACH POWDER, WATER, EGGS, SOYBEAN OIL, SALT. ORANGE DOUGH: ENRICHED DURUM WHEAT FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, FERROUS SULFATE, THIAMIN, MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WATER, EGGS, SOYBEAN OIL, OLEORESIN PAPRIKA, SALT. FILLING: CRACKER MEAL (BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR, WATER, SALT), PART SKIM RICOTTA CHEESE (PASTEURIZED PART SKIM MILK, STARTER, SALT), ROMANO CHEESE (PASTEURIZED SHEEP'S MILK, RENNET, BACTERIAL CULTURE, SALT), SOYBEAN OIL, SALT.
